thread.title: Roger Federer Again? It’s Getting Crazy

author: Jason Gay
title: Roger Federer Again? It’s Getting Crazy
text:
It’s supernutsobananas that we’re here again, but we’re here again.
Roger Federer has won another Grand Slam. This one, at age 102.
OK, so he’s 36. But you know what I mean. If you follow tennis, you did not see this coming a couple of years ago. After collecting a record 17 major tournaments, Federer cooled off as he entered his 30s. He...
